    "The reason for the use of this HMD is probably due to its popularity and it is not surprising that a few HMDs use it for 3DoF experiences.",
    "In addition, some equipment, such as eye-tracking sensors, is recommended for that type of Head Movement.",
    "With regard to 6DoF, it may first of all be noted that there is no consensus regarding the use of Gamepad locomotion, where all types of movement are used almost interchangeably, probably due to the age of the experiences.",
    "Secondly, Room scale is the type of interaction that follows the general statistics, with a majority use of 6DoF 360° external tracking, but being the most unusual type of interaction.",
    "Finally, Teleport locomotion is the most widely used type of interaction, making use of the most modern HMDs."
